than%20200%2C000%20customers%20between%20June%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20released%20Thursday%2C%20tracked%20where%20startups%20are%20spending%20their%20AI%20dollars%20and%20identified%20the%20top%2050%20AI-native%20application%20companies%20based%20on%20spending%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Ea16z%20said%20one%20category%20seeing%20a%20clear%20enterprise%20shift%20is%20%26quot%3Bvibe%20coding.%26quot%3B%20Startups%20are%20paying%20for%20apps%20that%20let%20anyone%20build%20software%20with%20prompts%20instead%20of%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%20coding%20tools%20like%20Replit%2C%20Cursor%2C%20Lovable%2C%20and%20Emergent%20ranked%20among%20the%20top%2050%20AI-native%20application%20companies.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EReplit%20placed%20third%20overall%20in%20total%20spend%20by%20Mercury%20users%2C%20right%20behind%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVibe%20coding%20is%20no%20mere%20consumer%20trend%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20landed%20in%20workplaces%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20three%20a16z%20staff%20who%20authored%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20interested%20in%20observing%20the%20vibe%20coding%20evolution%20over%20time.%20Will%20the%20space%20'fragment'%20through%20a%20rise%20of%20platforms%20for%20developing%20different%20types%20of%20applications%3F%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20horizontal%20AI%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20anyone%20in%20a%20company%20can%20use%2C%20from%20meeting%20copilots%20to%20general%20AI%20assistants%20%E2%80%94%20made%20up%20about%2060%25%20of%20the%20companies%20on%20the%20top-50%20list%2C%20compared%20with%2040%25%20for%20vertical%20tools%20built%20for%20specialized%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreative%20apps%20like%20Canva%20and%20ElevenLabs%2C%20along%20with%20vibe%20coding%20tools%2C%20fall%20into%20that%20horizontal%20category%2C%20a16z%20said.%20While%20creative%20tools%20were%20once%20reserved%20for%20marketing%20and%20design%20teams%20%E2%80%94%20and%20coding%20tools%20for%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20has%20made%20them%20accessible%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20has%20opened%20up%20applications%20in%20these%20categories%20that%20can%20be%20(and%20are)%20used%20by%20people%20in%20any%20role.%20We're%20seeing%20this%20in%20a%20few%20categories%2C%20where%20typically%20domain-specific%20tools%20are%20becoming%20more%20horizontal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Ea16z%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbb93d65-6ef9-4df2-b091-e149eb907353%5C%22%3EVibe%20coding%20is%20here%20to%20stay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%20coding%20has%20become%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-limits-learn-to-code-engineers-openai-microsoft-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley's%20favorite%20buzzwords%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20was%20coined%20in%20February%20by%20OpenAI%20cofounder%20Andrej%20Karpathy%2C%20who%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20kind%20of%20coding%26quot%3B%20where%20you%20%26quot%3Bfully%20give%20in%20to%20the%20vibes%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bforget%20that%20the%20code%20even%20exists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20marketable%20skill.%20Companies%20from%20Visa%20to%20Reddit%20to%20DoorDash%20have%20posted%20jobs%20that%20require%20vibe%20coding%20experience%20or%20familiarity%20with%20AI%20coding%20tools.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-candidates-use-ai-coding-interviews-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20said%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20allow%20job%20candidates%20to%20use%20an%20AI%20assistant%20in%20their%20coding%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20is%20following%20the%20momentum.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20July%2C%20Anysphere%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20Cursor%2C%20anno