%20of%20Utah.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208495fd3-b2d9-44a1-85ca-4c73e76d1cfa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETrading%20mountains%20for%20metropolis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESalt%20Lake%20City%20shaped%20us.%20It's%20where%20we%20met%2C%20built%20a%20community%2C%20and%20explored%20much%20of%20the%20American%20West.%20On%20weekends%2C%20we%20camped%20in%20national%20parks%20and%20hiked%20desert%20trails%20that%20felt%20like%20other%20worlds.%20Yet%2C%20daily%20life%20there%20could%20feel%20empty.%20Streets%20were%20quiet%20by%209%20pm%2C%20even%20on%20Fridays.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-from-texas-to-california-question-regret-move-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFinding%20events%20often%20took%20more%20effort%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20attending%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChicago%20was%20an%20immediate%20shock.%20We%20first%20lived%20in%20the%20downtown%20heart%20of%20the%20city%20(called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Loop%26quot%3B)%2C%20where%20fire%20truck%20sirens%20replaced%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20Wasatch%20foothills.%20Instead%20of%20hopping%20in%20a%20car%20to%20reach%20nature%2C%20we%20navigated%20packed%20trains%20and%20sidewalks.%20Learning%20the%20city%20meant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-from-moving-multiple-times-in-12-years-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elearning%20how%20to%20live%20around%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20lots%20of%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20first%2C%20it%20was%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20it%20also%20meant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-from-city-to-suburbs-why-ill-stay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enew%20experiences%20were%20always%20just%20outside%20our%20door%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20never%20more%20than%20one%2